'''Hélio Sandro Oliveira Alves Varela''' ({{IPA|pt|ˈɛ.li.u ˈsɐ̃.dɾu o.li.ˈvej.ɾɐ ˈal.vɨʒ vɐ.ˈɾɛ.lɐ|lang}}; born 3 May 2002) is a Cape Verdean professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Winger (association football)|winger]] for [[Israeli Premier League]] club [[Maccabi Tel Aviv F.C.|Maccabi Tel Aviv]]. Born in Portugal, Varela plays for the [[Cape Verde national football team|Cape Verde national team]].

==Club career==
Varela is a youth product of Monte Caparica, Charneca Caparica, [[Vitória F.C.|Vitória Setúbal]] and [[C.D. Cova da Piedade|Cova da Piedade]]. He began his senior career with [[Amora F.C.|Amora]] in 2020, before joining [[S.U. Sintrense|Sintrense]] for the 2021–22 [[Liga 3 (Portugal)|Liga 3]] season.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ojogo.pt/futebol/liga-3/noticias/liga-3-esta-mais-perto-da-ii-liga-do-que-do-campeonato-de-portugal-14024179.html|title="Liga 3 está mais perto da II Liga do que do Campeonato de Portugal"|date=August 11, 2021|website=www.ojogo.pt}}</ref> He moved to the reserves of [[Portimonense S.C.|Portimonense]] in the summer of 2022. He made his professional debut with them in a 0–0 (5–4) [[Taça da Liga]] penalty shootout loss to [[Leixões S.C.|Leixões]] on 30 July 2023.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://desporto.sapo.pt/futebol/jogo/leixoes-sc-vs-portimonense-767913|title=Leixões SC vs Portimonense|website=SAPO Desporto}}</ref> He scored his first league goal in a 1–1 [[Primeira Liga]] tie with [[F.C. Arouca|Arouca]] on 26 August 2023.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.noticiasaominuto.com/desporto/2387616/nasce-de-um-lancamento-lateral-helio-varela-adianta-assim-o-portimonense|title=Nasce de um lançamento lateral. Hélio Varela adianta assim o Portimonense|date=August 26, 2023|website=Notícias ao Minuto}}</ref>

On 16 August 2024, Varela joined [[K.A.A. Gent|Gent]].<ref>{{Cite web|url= https://www.kaagent.be/nl/nieuws/16-08-2024/helio-varela-versterkt-aanval-van-kaa-gent|title=Helio Varela versterkt aanval van KAA Gent|date=August 16, 2024|publisher= K.A.A. Gent|language=nl}}</ref> On 30 October, Varela made his debut with Gent in the [[Croky Cup]] against [[Union Rochefortoise]], he immediately scored 2 goals.

==International career==
Born in Portugal, Varela is of Cape Verdean descent. He was called up to the [[Cape Verde national football team|Cape Verde national team]] for a set of friendlies in October 2023.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.abola.pt/futebol/noticias/portimonense-helio-varela-em-estreia-na-selecao-de-cabo-verde-2023100516265875466|title=Portimonense: Hélio Varela em estreia na seleção de Cabo Verde &#124; Abola.pt|date=October 5, 2023|website=Abola.pt}}</ref> He debuted with Cape Verde as a substitute in a 5–1 friendly loss to [[Algeria national football team|Algeria]] on 12 October 2023.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.abola.pt/futebol/noticias/portimonense-primeira-internacionalizacao-para-helio-varela-2023101221281387569|title=Portimonense: primeira internacionalização para Hélio Varela &#124; Abola.pt|date=October 12, 2023|website=Abola.pt}}</ref>

